sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant Mercure as Mercure Hub
    participant Subscriber as Other client

    User->>Frontend: Type in message composer
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/channels/{id}/typing
    API->>API: Validate JWT and channel access
    API->>Mercure: Publish typing event
    Mercure-->>Subscriber: SSE typing update
    Subscriber->>Subscriber: Show typing indicator
